149 and $24,004 as of December 31, 2013 and 2012, respectively. Leased", "bbox": [162.5, 964.0, 1089.5, 984.8]}, {"text": "equipment includes amounts held under capital leases for automobiles, computer software and computer", "bbox": [162.5, 989.0, 1033.7, 1009.8]}, {"text": "equipment.", "bbox": [162.5, 1014.0, 255.7, 1034.8]}, {"text": "9.", "bbox": [162.5, 1079.3, 178.1, 1100.1]}, {"text": "Acquisitions:", "bbox": [199.0, 1079.3, 315.9, 1100.1]}, {"text": "2012 Acquisitions", "bbox": [183.3, 1118.0, 335.5, 1138.8]}, {"text": "On December 20, 2012, the Company acquired the net assets of Insurance Risk Management Solutions", "bbox": [225.0, 1156.4, 1084.7, 1177.2]}, {"text": "(“IRMS”). IRMS provided integrated property risk assessment technology underlying one of the Company’s", "bbox": [162.5, 1181.4, 1069.4, 1202.2]}, {"text": "geographic information system (“GIS”) underwriting solutions. At the end of 2012, the long-term contract with", "bbox": [162.5, 1206.4, 1092.3, 1227.2]}, {"text": "IRMS was expiring and precipitated a change in the business relationship. Instead of continuing forward with a", "bbox": [162.5, 1231.4, 1091.6, 1252.2]}, {"text": "new service agreement, the Company acquired IRMS as this will enable the Company to better manage, enhance", "bbox": [162.5, 1256.4, 1104.6, 1277.2]}, {"text": "and continue to use the solutions as part of its Risk Assessment segment. The Company paid a net cash purchase", "bbox": [162.5, 1281.4, 1102.4, 1302.2]}, {"text": "price of $26,422 and funded $1,000 of indemnity escrows. The preliminary purchase price allocation of the", "bbox": [162.5, 1306.4, 1058.4, 1327.2]}, {"text": "acquisition is presented as “Others” in the table below.", "bbox": [162.5, 1331.4, 619.9, 1352.2]}, {"text": "On August 31, 2012, the Company acquired Argus Information & Advisory Services, LLC (“Argus”), a", "bbox": [225.0, 1383.4, 1092.6, 1404.2]}, {"text": "provider of information, competitive benchmarking, scoring solutions, analytics, and customized services to", "bbox": [162.5, 1408.4, 1065.3, 1429.2]}, {"text": "financial institutions and regulators in North America, Latin America, and Europe, for a net cash purchase price", "bbox": [162.5, 1433.4, 1096.2, 1454.2]}, {"text": "78", "bbox": [627.1, 1484.1, 647.9, 1504.9]}]}